  "translations": {
    "en": "When this verse was revealed to the Messenger of Allah (peace be upon him and his family), he went out reciting it and smiling. He said to his companions: Who will direct me to that repentant youth? Mu'adh said: O Messenger of Allah, we were told he is in such-and-such place. So the Messenger of Allah (peace be upon him and his family) went with his companions until they reached that mountain. They climbed it searching for the youth, and there they found the youth standing between two rocks, his hands bound to his neck, his face blackened, his eyelashes fallen from weeping, and he was saying:",
